name: Prophetess (V)
Lore: 'Renowned female psychic. Predictor of doom. Agent for Governor Aryon of Tatooine. Tailed Jabba and his thugs to Docking Bay 94 when they confronted Han Solo.',
Text: 'Deploy -1 and forfeit +3 at a site. Once per turn, may peek at top card of opponent''s Reserve Deck or Used Pile; may then shuffle that Reserve Deck or Used Pile. Immune to attrition < 3.',
